select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN M.NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY_COUNT from CP1UNCTMEMBER M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN M.RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP_COUNT, CASE WHEN M.JOINT_WORKPLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as JOINT_WORKPLAN_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1INTERAGENCY_GROUP M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN M.DAO = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1COUNTRY M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select CP1.ID, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN cp1.DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP_COUNT, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_NO, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_NO, HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID, HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID, HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID, HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID, HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID, HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID, HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID, HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID, HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID, HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID, HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID, HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID, HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID, cp1joint.GOVERNMENT_ROLE_ID, CASE WHEN cp1joint.HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW, CASE WHEN cp1annual.REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV, CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.BUDGETED_WORKPLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as BUDGETED_WORKPLAN from CP1GENERAL_PROFILE cp1, CP1JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN cp1joint, CP1ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS cp1annual, CP1JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY cp1jointstrategy, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE cp1joint.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND cp1annual.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND cp1jointstrategy.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR
